The paper deals with video understanding, specifically in the context of captioning and question answering. This suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories, including computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and multimedia (cs.MM). Among these, computer vision and natural language processing are the most likely categories, as they are directly related to the tasks of captioning and question answering.
